        .heavy.col-md-4
          Have an Omnibus package?
          %h5.title Used our package server on Ubuntu / Debian?
          %p.answer
            %code
              sudo apt-get update
            %br
            %code
              sudo apt-get install gitlab-ce
          %h5.title Used our package server on CentOS?
          %p.answer
            %code
              sudo yum install gitlab-ce
          %h5.title Want to upgrade from a manually downloaded Omnibus package to package server?
          %p.answer
            %a.view-docs{href: "/upgrade-to-package-repository"} View our documentation on upgrading to the package repository
          %h5.title Want to keep using manually downloaded Omnibus packages?
          %p.answer
            %a.view-docs{href: "https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/omnibus-gitlab/blob/master/doc/update/README.md#updating-from-gitlab-66-and-higher-to-the-latest-version"} View documentation here
