          %h5.title Want to stay on source?
          %p.answer 
            For patch updates visit our 
            %a.view-docs{href: "https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab-ce/blob/master/doc/update/patch_versions.md"} universal update guide for patch versions
            %br 
            %br
